  "The Dashboard and Health Score above are live previews. Browse every tool below, grouped by what it does — some need your app running with the Drift debug server connected.": "上述的控制台和健康分數為實時預覽。請瀏覽下方每一個工具，這些工具按功能分組——有些需要您的應用程式正在運行且Driftdebug伺服器已連接。",
  "The debug server exposes your whole database, so by default it binds to 127.0.0.1 (loopback) only — reachable from this machine, not from any other host on your network. To reach it from a physical device by its LAN IP, start it with loopbackOnly: false and set an authToken.": "调试伺服器會公開整個資料庫，因此預設僅綁定至 127.0.0.1（回圈網）——只能從此主機訪問，而無法從網路中的其他主機訪問。如需透過局域網路 IP 從物理裝置存取伺服器，請以 loopbackOnly: false 開始並設定 authToken。",
  "The emulator runs in a separate network namespace. The extension automatically tries adb forward when a debug session starts, but you can also do it manually:": "模拟器運行在獨立的網路命名空間中。擴展程式會在開始除錯會話時自動嘗試 adb 前置，但您也可以手動執行此步驟：",
  "The extension is connected to your app and serving live data.": "擴展功能已連接到您的應用程式並提供實時數據。",
  "The extension uses two connection methods:": "該擴展使用兩種連接方法：",
  "The global kill switch is engaged — nothing is recorded and data endpoints answer 403.": "全球緊急開關已啟用—無資料記錄且數據端點回應403。",
  "The global kill switch is engaged: no query recording, no diagnostics, no background sweeps. Data endpoints on the Drift debug server answer 403 until monitoring is resumed.": "全球緊急開關已啟用：不記錄查詢，無診斷功能，無背景掃描。在監控恢復之前，Drift 調試伺服器上的資料端點回應 403。",
  "The server may not be ready yet; try <strong>Retry Connection</strong> after a few seconds": "伺服器可能尚未準備好；幾秒後試著再連一次<strong>重試連接</strong>。",
  "The sidebar remembered your database structure from the last connection and is showing it from a workspace cache. Table and column names are real, but there is no live data and the row counts are stale. Reconnect to the running app to load live data.": "Sidebar 记住了上次连接时的資料庫結構，並從工作區緩存中顯示它。表和欄位名稱是真實的，但沒有實時數據且行數已過時。重新連接到運行中的應用程式以加載實時數據。",
  "The target snapshot to compare against": "與比較對象的目標快照",
  "This project uses the Saropa Lints package, but the Saropa Lints extension is not installed — it adds static Drift rules and quick fixes alongside Drift Advisor. Install it?": "這個專案使用了SaropaLint套件，但未安裝SaropaLint擴展—它會添加靜態Drift規則和快速修復功能，與Drift顧問一同工作。是否安裝？",
  "This project uses the Saropa Log Capture package, but the Saropa Log Capture extension is not installed — it records the logs, crashes, and slow queries behind Drift Advisor findings. Install it?": "這個專案使用了Saropa Log Capture 套件，但未安裝Saropa Log Capture 擴展——它記錄了Drift顧問發現背後的日誌、 Crash 和慢查詢。是否安裝？",
